[section#cpp.module
    [:en] Module directive
    [:zh_CN] 模块指令

[%  [:en] preprocessing directive[!module]
    [:zh_CN] 预处理指令[!模块] ]
]

[syntax]
[rule pp-module [:zh_CN] 预处理模块 ]
    [| [`:opt:key export] [`:key module] [~:opt pp-tokens] new-line ]
[rule:end]
[syntax:end]

[para]
[:en] The [~pp-tokens], if any, of a [~pp-module] shall be of the form:
[:zh_CN] [~预处理模块]的[~预处理记号序列]（如果有）应当为如下形式：
[syntax:explanation]
[~pp-module-name] [~:opt pp-module-partition] [~:opt pp-tokens]
[syntax:end]
[:en@~] where the grammar non-terminals are defined as:
[:zh_CN] 其中各个文法非终结符定义如下：

[syntax:explanation]
[rule pp-module-name [:zh_CN] 预处理模块名 ]
    [| [~:opt pp-module-name-qualifier] identifier ]
[rule:end]
[rule pp-module-partition [:zh_CN] 预处理模块分区 ]
    [| [`:] [~:opt pp-module-name-qualifier] identifier ]
[rule:end]
[rule pp-module-name-qualifier [:zh_CN] 预处理模块名限定符 ]
    [| identifier [`.] ]
    [| pp-module-name-qualifier identifier [`.] ]
[rule:end]
[syntax:end]

[:en] No [~identifier] in the [~pp-module-name] or [~pp-module-partition]
shall currently be defined as an object-like macro or followed by [`(] as the
next preprocessing token at the start of phase 4 of translation ([#lex.phases]).
[:zh_CN] [~预处理模块名]或[~预处理模块分区]中的[~标识符]都不能当前被定义为对象式宏
或者在翻译阶段 4（[#lex.phases]）开始时后面跟随的下一个预处理记号是 [`(]。

[para]
[:en] Any preprocessing tokens after the [`module] preprocessing token in the
[`module] directive are processed just as in normal text.
[:zh_CN] [`module] 指令中的预处理记号 [`module] 之后的任何预处理记号仅被当做普通文本处理。

[begin:note]
[:en] Each identifier currently defined as a macro name is replaced by its
replacement list of preprocessing tokens.
[:zh_CN] 每个当前已被定义为宏名的标识符均被替换为其预处理记号替换列表。
[end:note]

[para]
[:en] The [`module] and [`export] (if it exists) preprocessing tokens are replaced
by the [~module-keyword] and [~export-keyword] preprocessing tokens respectively.
[:zh_CN] 预处理记号 [`module] 和 [`export]（若其存在）被分别替换为预处理记号
[~模块关键词]和[~导出关键词]。

[begin:note]
[:en] This makes the line no longer a directive so it is not removed at the end of phase 4.
[:zh_CN] 这使代码行不再是一条指令，因而不会在阶段 4 末尾被移除。
[end:note]

[:en] After this replacement, the preprocessing tokens that constituted the
directive are a [~text-line] and are processed as normal text.
[:zh_CN] 这项替换后，构成指令的预处理记号是一个[~文本行]并按普通文本处理。

[begin:note]
[:en] No macro expansion is possible for the [~pp-module-name] and [~pp-module-partition].
[:zh_CN] 宏展开不可能为[~预处理模块名]和[~预处理模块分区]。
[end:note]

[:en] After such processing, there shall be a [`;] or [``[] preprocessing token
following the [~pp-module-name] and optional [~pp-module-partition].
[:zh_CN] 经过这些处理后，[~预处理模块名]和可选的[~预处理模块分区]之后应当跟着
预处理记号 [`;] 或 [``[]。

[para]
[begin:example]
[:en] Importable header [`"common.h"]:
[:zh_CN] 可导入头文件 [`"common.h"]：
[codeblock]
#define DOT_BAR .bar
#define MOD_ATTR [[vendor::shiny_module]]
[codeblock:end]

[para:~]
[:en] Translation unit [`#1]:
[:zh_CN] 翻译单元 [`#1]：
[codeblock]
module;
#include "common.h"

export module foo DOT_BAR;      // [:en] error: expansion of [`DOT_BAR;] does not begin with [`;] or [``[] \
                                [:zh_CN] 错误：[`DOT_BAR;] 的展开并不以 [`;] 或 [``[] 开头
[codeblock:end]

[para:~]
[:en] Translation unit [`#2]:
[:zh_CN] 翻译单元 [`#2]：
[codeblock]
module;
#include "common.h"

export module M MOD_ATTR ;      // OK
[codeblock:end]
[end:example]

[para:~]
[begin:example]
[codeblock]
export module a
.b;                             // [:en] error: preprocessing token after [~pp-module-name] is not [`;] or [``[] \
                                [:zh_CN] 错误：[~预处理模块名]之后的预处理记号不是 [`;] 或 [``[]
[codeblock:end]
[end:example]

[para:~]
[begin:example]
[codeblock]
export module M [[
attr1,
attr2 ]] ;                      // OK
[codeblock:end]
[end:example]

[para:~]
[begin:example]
[codeblock]
export module M
[[ attr1,
attr2 ]] ;                      // OK
[codeblock:end]
[end:example]

[para:~]
[begin:example]
[codeblock]
export module M; int
n;                              // OK
[codeblock:end]
[end:example]
